{"title":"十三陵水库工地短诗","authors":[],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":4,"day":7}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"十三陵水库工地短诗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十三陵水库工地的贴报牌上有一些短诗，抄录如下："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热血战胜三九天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手改造大自然"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"修成水库制洪水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从今旱地变水田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劈山筑坝下水冰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"运石担土快如风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白天红旗飘百面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜里灯光万点星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月亮当太阳"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沙土当纸张"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"水库修建成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"文盲也扫光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烟土飞扬天昏暗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚石奔腾河水翻"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"炮声威震悬崖倒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗招展笑声欢"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手劈开天寿山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三十万亩不靠天"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}